data.description: Discover the charm of this newly renovated single-story residence located in the desirable Rancho Belago Community of Moreno Valley. This home has been thoughtfully updated with a fresh coat of paint and features a spacious layout that spans 2,378 sqft, including 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The inviting kitchen flows seamlessly into a welcoming family room, complete with a warm fireplace, making it an ideal space for hosting. Elegantly accented with crown molding and vibrant new paint throughout, the layout ensures privacy with the master suite positioned apart from the other bedrooms. The master suite itself is a retreat, boasting a large walk-in closet and a luxurious bathroom with dual vanities, a walk-in shower, and a soaking tub.  One of the standout features is an additional room that currently serves as an office but can easily be converted into a 4th bedroom, playroom, or another office, offering flexible options for growing families or changing needs.  Outside, the backyard is beautifully landscaped with an array of mature fruit trees—pomegranate, orange, fig, and peach. A 3-car tandem garage provides ample storage and has been cleverly utilized to include an air-conditioned office space, adding functionality to this already impressive home. Additionally, there's a separate, external office space, also with air conditioning, perfect for those requiring a quiet, dedicated work area.  Enjoy the benefits of a low HOA fee and close proximity to essential amenities such as hospitals, parks, and shops.
